recipe.label: Thai Fried Rice recipes
ingredientLines: 4 to 8 cloves garlic, minced (or more if not using optional ingredients)
1 to 2 ounces thinly sliced boneless pork (optional)
2 cups cold cooked rice (preferably Thai jasmine)
1 cup torn Asian greens (such as cabbage, mustard greens, or bok choy)
2 teaspoons Thai fish sauce, or to taste
1 small scallion, trimmed and thinly sliced on the bias (optional)
1/4 cup Thai Fish Sauce with Hot Chiles

recipe.label: Asian Peanut Noodles recipes
ingredientLines: 1 medium carrot, peeled and thinly sliced crosswise
12 ounces dried soba or udon noodles
18 sprigs fresh cilantro, long stems removed
2/3 cup natural peanut butter (no added sugar)

1 medium red bell pepper, cored, seeded, and sliced into 1/2-inch strips
1/2 medium English cucumber, thinly sliced crosswise
